videos.headline: 75-yard QB run sets up Troy's opening TD
videos.description: Kaleb Barker takes off down the sideline and gets all the way to the 4-yard line, setting up B.J. Smith's 2-yard touchdown run to make it 7-0 Trojans.

videos.headline: Barker throws strike for 2nd TD pass of game
videos.description: Kaleb Barker connects with WR Deondre Douglas for a 12-yard touchdown pass, extending Troy's lead to 21-0.

videos.headline: Troy WR drops easy TD and gifts Georgia State a takeaway
videos.description: Tray Eafford makes an inexcusable drop, and incidentally knocks the ball into the hands of a trailing Panthers DB.

videos.headline: Troy widens lead with 41-yard TD pass
videos.description: QB Sawyer Smith  drops a dime to WR Damion Willis, who dives for the pylon and makes it 30-6 Trojans.

videos.headline: Troy puts on finishing touches with 78-yard TD run
videos.description: RB B.J. Smith finds a seam and outruns the defense all the way to the end zone, making it 37-12 Trojans late in the 4th quarter.
